{
  "stem": "21582.5",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Sometimes they would appear, the Germans would appear, and it was a response.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Sometimes it was a response to the Germans and sometimes it was provoked by the-- by the partisans.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Now, I think that the partisans wanted in some way to send out a message to the Germans.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "It's not so safe to come in anymore into that little enclave that was left.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "So I guess at that point they invited sometimes confrontations and they-- they-- they used a ruse.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "They-- they would lure them in.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Now, up until then the Germans, why, there was still a certain amount of fear of being attacked, because they were sporadic times.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "But, you know, they were very-- they were very unapproachable.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Because even I remember having the fantasy-- and my sister, and my mother, we shared it-- we wanted a job, but you knew that there's always the gun between-- between you and that physical person that you wanted to attack.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "So you can always be blown away, and there-- there-- there is-- there is no resistance in that.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "So-- so-- so the Germans did have a certain fear.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Now at this point, when these confrontations occurred, they were much more cautious.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "They could not-- they were not total-- totally in control.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "They could not go in-- into the ghetto, step in-- into the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "You know, the buildings were not dense.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "It was not that every apartment was occupied.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "There were only-- you know, you could be shot.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "They had the freedom, the-- the-- the partisans, the-- the run of the whole building.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And if they would go into-- if the Germans would go into one-- so many apartments would be empty.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "They never knew where one was lurking.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "They sometimes would lure them up to-- to the attics.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
